('d58d6584-2883-5b89-bde6-56e47c73f323', 'edbe2b73-92ca-4fb5-b2f0-f51b9596ea32', 'My sister likes to ___ her bedroom with many cute posters.', '我妹妹喜歡用許多可愛的海報來佈置她的臥室。', 'decorate', 'wash', 'forget', 'teach', 'root ''decor'' 意指裝飾、風格。', 'decorate → 裝飾。想像把房間弄得很漂亮。', '2026-07-07 03:08:59', '2026-07-07 03:08:59'),
('951a4f74-e179-5f2e-8582-cb451d8e10bb', '0a9d1fff-48a1-407a-8876-f4f1e5167e0a', 'The old box contained a wonderful ___.', '那個舊盒子包含了一個很棒的發現。', 'find', 'song', 'desk', 'milk', 'find 為名詞，意為「發現物」。', 'find → 發現出的寶物 (a great find)', '2026-07-07 11:56:30', '2026-07-07 11:56:30'),
('601b8b86-03dc-5dab-aea1-fc050e277957', 'd9ae7a17-bdfa-436d-abd7-fe52549f4090', 'Please don''t ___ to bring your textbook tomorrow.', '明天請不要忘記帶你的課本。', 'forget', 'start', 'stop', 'want', 'forget 為單純動詞，無明顯詞根詞綴。', 'for- 有強調之意 + get (得到) → 強調原本得到的東西變不見了 → 忘記。', '2026-07-07 12:38:28', '2026-07-07 12:38:28'),
('fbda8b90-4b77-52d4-83d1-b53ac9c0c223', '49c868ce-5483-438c-92c9-f6e1fcc738cf', 'I often help my ___ water the flowers in her garden.', '我經常幫我的祖母在她的花園裡澆花。', 'grandma', 'brother', 'neighbor', 'student', 'grand (大的/偉大的) + ma (媽媽的口語用法)', '想像一位很偉大 (grand) 的媽媽 (ma) → 祖母', '2026-07-08 06:18:19', '2026-07-08 06:18:19'),
('c6480133-d086-58f6-b8af-0e931450142b', 'aa0dee8b-f583-48b2-a630-5e77d7571b6a', 'I ___ eating vegetables when I was a little kid.', '我小時候很討厭吃蔬菜。', 'hate', 'love', 'like', 'want', 'hate 為基礎單字，表示強烈的厭惡。', '想像看到不喜歡的蔬菜時，心裡大喊 Hate!', '2026-07-07 14:38:32', '2026-07-07 14:38:32');
